## Stop an app

```
Definition
```

```http
PUT /v3/apps/:guid/stop HTTP/1.1
```

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.[your-domain.com]/v3/apps/[guid]/stop" \
  -X PUT \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK

<%= yield_content :app_with_state, 'STOPPED' %>
```

This endpoint stops a running app.


